
<html>
<head>
	<title>Password Reminder</title>
</head>

<body>
<blockquote><font face="arial" size=2>
Forgot your password?  Have your password e-mailed to you by entering your username and e-mail address 
in the form below.
</font></blockquote><br>

<form action="~script_name~" method="POST">
<table border=1 cellspacing=2 cellpadding=2 width=60% align=center>
<tr>
	<th width=100% colspan=2 bgcolor="#888888"><font face="arial" size=3 color="#FFFFFF">Password Reminder</font></th>
</tr><tr>
	<td><font face="arial" size=2>Username:</font></td>
	<td><input type="text" name="username" size=25></td>
</tr><tr>
	<td><font face="arial" size=2>E-Mail Address:</font></td>
	<td><input type="text" name="email" size=25></td>
</tr><tr>
	<td width=100% colspan=2 align=center><font face="arial" size=2>
	<input type="submit" value="E-Mail My Password">
	<input type="reset" value="Clear Fields">
	</font></td>
</tr></table></form>

</body>
</html>

